      "description": "### What's New in v1.4.1\r\n- Scoped conversion to Obsidian's active editor event (fully fixed search bar/settings collisions!).\r\n- Rewritten chemistry parser to eliminate false positives on plain English words (like \"He\" or \"In\").\r\n- Added nested fractions, smart multiplication context, and mobile-friendly keyboard handling.\r\n- Fixed math block parsing ($$ and $) to prevent double conversion.",
