      "author": "katananananna",
      "description": "### What's New in v1.4.0\r\n\r\n- **Improved Focus Bug:** The shorthand converter now only runs when actively typing in your note editor (it will no longer accidentally trigger when typing in the search bar or settings).\r\n- **Added Missing Symbols:** Added shorthand support for `<-` (left arrow), `=<` (less than or equal to), and `-+` (minus-plus symbol).\r\n- **Cleaner Math Loops:** Optimized how formatting matches occur under the hood so your notes load smoothly without any lag!",
